:: Head to the closet. {"position":"800,850","size":"100,100"}
Looking around your white-lined navy royal green room. It's plain, but it isn't meant to be.  You try not to think about it too much. 

You touch a part of the wall

It opens lie a giant touch screen, but opens up from left to right. You smile.

You have a couple of options. 

The screen lights up. Several options appear like a character selection screen.
A fancy suit that can fit any situation with a touch of a coller, and can change slightly to personalize the wearer. A classic wear-everywhere, casual wear. And finally, something in betwen. Not too fancy, but not too casual. Sort of plain in color, but makes up for it wih a sharp cuff style.

